    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the grill to high</p><p>Take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Top, tail and slice your <strong>courgette[s]</strong> on a diagonal</p><p>Deseed your <strong>pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thick strips</p>",
