    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>courgette slices</strong>, <strong>pepper strips</strong>, <strong>tomato wedges </strong>and <strong>onion</strong> <strong>wedges </strong>to a large tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] under the<strong> </strong>grill for 8-10 min or until softened and charred – these are your <strong>grilled vegetables</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
