    {
      "instruction": "<p>In a small bowl, combine your <strong>green tomato chutney</strong> with the juice of <strong>half </strong>your<strong> lemon[s]</strong>,<strong> </strong>2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your<strong> green tomato dressing</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
